dc_description_s: This data represents hydrography (polygon) for Shawano County, Wisconsin in 2022. [The data in this layer are a representation of the surface water bodies in Shawano County. The water bodies may be registered with the Wisconsin Department of Natural Resources, but many are not. The water bodies were digitized using six inch pixel orthophotograchic images (2015 and 2010) and LiDAR (2015). The layer is updated as new information becomes available.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison.
